{"tid":909620,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打試過記實報稅表俾人罰錢？","createTime":"2018-11-20T13:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T15:48:41.000Z","uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9933849b57d5a511f3ec40ee7600cb775ec661b","tid":909620,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日收到稅局封信話我之前有份稅表冇收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我期期都寄足有機會寄失咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個情況下除咗逼住交罰款之外仲有冇其他方法<br />\n唔想冇啦啦比人罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打試過咁情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rhdKbr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rhdKbr.png&h=74188272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fac682adf3b4e64ff1027721295523f449aaef6","tid":909620,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"打錯topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寄失報稅表先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9225277ad20d4c5e2870a9335a03725133380a","tid":909620,"uid":35818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"打電話上稅局叫佢出過份比你填<br />\n唔好簽回條，反轉背面白紙寫低：已貼足郵票，不知是否寄失，要求取消罰款，簽名<br />\n收到報稅表之後一齊寄<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：郵費最少兩蚊，摺得厚啲可能會變$3.4，垃圾郵局on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3beb65a030af546814f22ffa586108edbf7950","tid":909620,"uid":95663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"前排搞完，要去灣仔稅務大樓攞幾份表，填完再加張自己寫既解釋信一齊寄過去"},{"pid":"bd8d4a25b7f6f4edb43915fbb317acc0c2fcf514","tid":909620,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"唔該樓上巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"